metadata.name: Coral Reefer #1
metadata.description: The Coral Reefers is a CO2 neutral, generative collection has five unique digital collectable forms on three different background colours (white, black and gradient) that evolves on a human form over the course of 6 weeks or seven generations. Coral Reefers raises funds to restore real world coral reefs, home to over a million species and critical to restoring ocean health, an essential component to turning the tide on the climate crisis.
